{"tid":486381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果老屈非禮犯做強姦犯","createTime":"2017-12-01T19:04:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-02T06:15:39.000Z","uid":121961,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"adb2355174babed877587f45f87bc358bde96eab","tid":486381,"uid":121961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T19:04:15.000Z","msg":"<strong>過來人公開經歷 後悔拒出庭放生強姦犯</strong><br />\n<br />\n9年前，月心收到異性朋友的一通電話，「佢話唔開心，想傾偈，一男一女，飲咗一陣，佢就強行&hellip;&hellip;侵犯咗我。」該名「朋友」是她投身職場後認識，案發時相識已有5年，「當時感到佢係正經、好好人，唔會毛手毛腳&hellip;&hellip;係可以信任嘅朋友。」<br />\n但9年前的某天，她如常應約到該男性「朋友」寓所作客，各自喝下幾罐啤酒，「朋友」狼性盡露，「其實當時我仲係清醒，不過就&hellip;&hellip;」她說，事後一輪哭啼後，才感到害怕，「感覺好驚、唔知點做，覺得自己好污糟」。她曾懼怕舉報強姦犯會惹來「自己攞嚟衰」等指摘，但經過一輪思想掙扎，翌日決定致電關注團體風雨蘭求助，甚至出庭控告加害者。<span style=\"color: red;\">結果該位「朋友」強姦罪成，判監5年。<br />\n「不過兩年後佢申請上訴，（法庭）要發還重審，法院叫我再上庭作供。我唔肯。」她解釋，事隔兩年，被強姦當日的記憶早已淡化，上庭等於要在加害者面前再次述說那段痛苦的經歷，她斷言拒絕。最後「朋友」被法庭改判非禮罪，扣減已服刑期後，當庭釋放。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">法庭已經改判左做非禮罪，蘋果仲叫人做強姦犯。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"b30b06f580e954d4adacb9b69f98aa4a90e1a893","tid":486381,"uid":121961,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T19:04:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171202/57530268\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171202%2F57530268&d=y6AftZrosRa1SWwQALRMaf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=6dd494a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171202%2F57530268&h=4139c980\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171202/57530268</a>"},{"pid":"b6faa5701d39aa3a68a3cd3dd7f56ca19d846151","tid":486381,"uid":92459,"like":17,"dislike":4,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T19:12:49.000Z","msg":"人地係fb打篇文，<br />\n蘋果都已經作好標題，寫埋感想<br />\n然後下面一堆留言寫咩好勇敢，唔好懷疑人，好地地點會屈佢，教練乜乜乜<br />\n我睇完留言仲以為個教練已經判完坐緊監呀<br />\n惡過共產黨"},{"pid":"57cbb4a283424ab63f21b68abae30a31020fbc2a","tid":486381,"uid":121961,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T19:15:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地係fb打篇文，<br />\n蘋果都已經作好標題，寫埋感想<br />\n然後下面一堆留言寫咩好勇敢，唔好懷疑人，好地地點會屈佢，教練乜乜乜<br />\n我睇完留言仲以為個教練已經判完坐緊監呀<br />\n惡過共產黨</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔小心負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9cbf5cd68382090e66161b7a784faaaeab227f","tid":486381,"uid":6347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T19:44:23.000Z","msg":"呢件事睇到呢個世界啲人真係痴線架"},{"pid":"7f74275fde99be088e621a55e0784f8db8ea5a7c","tid":486381,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T19:57:17.000Z","msg":"邊個editor <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bebf7699b729c0e45be9f586563839909ee5922","tid":486381,"uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T19:57:53.000Z","msg":"樓主文盲定乜，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb5dd56b156c3a6bea417a2ad296fa720606059","tid":486381,"uid":121961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T20:06:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主文盲定乜，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊到文盲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4101969a39d6f36c4ae64334cf580943cd97a3a","tid":486381,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T20:08:12.000Z","msg":"恭喜道德上訴庭推翻法院判決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30648772a6ec6fc292810289129d4297e111e885","tid":486381,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T23:42:18.000Z","msg":"唔理個事實係點,佢唔上庭嗰一刻就已經輸咗"},{"pid":"434a11dbd59105ce6ee10e1424275053b46447e5","tid":486381,"uid":55533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T23:45:46.000Z","msg":"毒果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"643c812399a0ebd781c8cd208eed6f8f1df698ce","tid":486381,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T23:58:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔理個事實係點,佢唔上庭嗰一刻就已經輸咗</blockquote><br />\n想知 當年單野係乜先 人地上訴改判非禮 姐係扑都冇扑過 又話強姦傷害大 但兩年就淡化左<br />\n強姦同非禮 搵個毒撚知咩事 強姦咁輕易推翻 強姦多數有決定性證物 精液 原審係冇呢樣證物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  上訢庭有乜可能有精液判決下推翻強姦 定一開始原判已經係判錯"},{"pid":"3b9eb0a7a2cc90c58e8a32efc23055f97f8622f9","tid":486381,"uid":121961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T06:14:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔理個事實係點,佢唔上庭嗰一刻就已經輸咗</blockquote><br />\n想知 當年單野係乜先 人地上訴改判非禮 姐係扑都冇扑過 又話強姦傷害大 但兩年就淡化左<br />\n強姦同非禮 搵個毒撚知咩事 強姦咁輕易推翻 強姦多數有決定性證物 精液 原審係冇呢樣證物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  上訢庭有乜可能有精液判決下推翻強姦 定一開始原判已經係判錯</blockquote><br />\n事主話強姦經歷太痛苦 唔想上庭諗返起痛苦經歷喎"},{"pid":"35c377524134df1274c6966b7be4bff21e583055","tid":486381,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T06:15:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}